testRun [options] [submitDir]

USAGE:
$testRun [options] [submitDir]
Use options to specify which driver will be used.
Place list of files in <working directory>/FileList.txt

ARGUMENTS:
submitDir: specify submit directory.

OPTIONS:
Choose MC matching algorithm. Auto (TruthLink) or manual (dR):
-a: Auto MC match (default)
-m: Manual MC match

Choose ONE driver:
-b: Lxbatch (LSF driver)
-g: GRID (Grid Driver)
-d: direct (direct driver)


-f: specify number of files per worker node on batch, defaults to 15:
	testRun -f 8 submitDir

-n: specify number of events to run on, default no limit:
	testRun -n 2500 submitDir
